==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Double-bank
<hw>Dou"ble-bank"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>To row by rowers sitting side by side in twos on a bank or
thwart.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>To double-bank an oar</b></col>, <cd>to set two men to
pulling one oar.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Double-banked</ent>⟦br⟧
